text: Baoquan () is a town in Kedong County, western Heilongjiang province, Northeast China, located on a tributary of the Nonni River more than east- northeast of the city of Qiqihar. China National Highway 202 (G202) passes through the town, which is down the road from the city of Bei'an and the county seat, which lies some to the south. ==External links== *Official website of Baoquan Town Government Category:Township-level divisions of Heilongjiang
title: Baoquan, Heilongjiang
